STATE of North Carolina
v.
Darrian DeLOACH. No. 311P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 29, 2006. Darrian DeLoatch, Pro Se. William P. Hart, Senior Deputy Attorney General, Thomas J. Keith, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 13th day of June 2006 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Forsyth County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 29th day of June 2006."
